==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Motoring
<hw>Mo"tor*ing</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>the act or
recreation of riding in or driving a motor car or automobile.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>Webster 1913 Suppl.</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Motoring</ent>⟦br⟧

==== ENTRY 2 ====
HEADWORD: Motoring
<hw>Mo"tor*ing</hw>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Pertaining to motor cars or
automobiles, or to the technology of such; addicted to riding in or
driving automobiles; <as>as, <ex>motoring</ex> parlance; my
<ex>motoring</ex> friend</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>Webster 1913 Suppl.</source>]</p>

<p><ent>motorisation</ent>⟦br⟧
